            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01JdM3PSpXAQufjn3DywhCwq\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I appreciate the enthusiasm, but let's stay focused! 😊\\n\\nYou just told me about **Friend of the Pod**—a podcast matchmaking service. That's a real business idea with potential. Now I need you to help me understand what makes it special.\\n\\nHere's what I need to know:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Let's flesh out your podcast matchmaking idea. I need to understand the core business model and what makes Friend of the Pod different.\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"Who are you matching? (e.g., podcast hosts with guests, listeners with shows, creators with collaborators)\\\",\\n    \\\"What problem does it solve? (e.g., 'Hosts struggle to find quality guests in their niche' or 'Podcasters are lonely and need co-host partners')\\\",\\n    \\\"What's your unfair advantage? (e.g., 'We use AI to match based on audience demographics' or 'We have a community of 10,000+ verified podcasters')\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Give me 2-3 sentences about what Friend of the Pod does and why it's better than alternatives. That's all I need to move forward.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2546,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":280,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
