            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1767,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01Jhao629v7wk5jZdVjRwLws\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I appreciate you wanting to move forward, but I need to understand your core business idea first—it's the foundation for everything else we'll build.\\n\\nLet me help you think through this. A great business idea answers:\\n- **What problem do you solve?** (or what do you help people achieve?)\\n- **What makes you different?** (why you, not someone else?)\\n\\nHere are some examples of solid ideas:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"I can't skip this one—your business idea is the foundation for your entire landing page. Let's nail this together. Think about: What problem do you solve, or what do you help people achieve? And what makes your approach different?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"A meal prep service for busy professionals that uses AI to personalize weekly menus based on dietary preferences and fitness goals—saving them 5+ hours per week\\\",\\n    \\\"A B2B SaaS tool that helps e-commerce brands reduce cart abandonment by 40% through personalized exit-intent offers powered by behavioral data\\\",\\n    \\\"A coaching program for mid-career professionals pivoting to tech, with a focus on landing jobs in 90 days through a peer-cohort model (vs. traditional 1-on-1 coaching)\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"What's your idea? Don't worry about it being perfect—just give me the core concept and what makes it different.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2299,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":326,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
