            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1503,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_013whN5bjGgF6EjMbg2HzboN\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I appreciate the enthusiasm, but I need to actually understand your business idea first! I can't build great marketing copy without knowing what you're selling and who you're selling it to.\\n\\nLet me ask you directly: **What's your business idea?** What problem are you solving, or what are you offering?\\n\\nHere are some examples of what I'm looking for:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"I need to understand your core business idea before we can move forward. What problem does your business solve, or what are you offering to customers?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"An AI-powered meal planning app that creates personalized weekly menus based on dietary restrictions and grocery prices in your area\\\",\\n    \\\"A B2B software platform that helps small law firms automate contract review and reduce turnaround time by 70%\\\",\\n    \\\"A luxury pet grooming service that comes to your home, so busy professionals don't have to spend hours at a salon\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Tell me what your business does and what makes it different from what's already out there.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2309,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":250,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
